# =============================================================================
# What's hidden:
#   - LaTeX source + build artifacts (kept local in */admin/)
#   - Makefile and build scripts (kept local)
#   - Toolchain binaries (install locally under repos/)
#   - Private scratch (supplementary/, **/admin/, .claude/)
# What's tracked:
#   - PDFs (the products)
#   - examples/ source (Verilog, schematics, YAML)
#   - images in each section (used by the PDFs)
#   - README files explaining each top-level directory
# =============================================================================

# Private / scratch
supplementary/
.claude/
**/admin/

# TA-only materials (kept local, not published)
ta/

# LaTeX source — kept local inside admin/, never in git
*.tex
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*.nav
*.snm
*.synctex.gz
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk

# Build tooling — local only
Makefile
*.py
__pycache__/

# Python virtual envs
venv/
.venv/

# Toolchain binaries (install locally under repos/)
repos/oss-cad-suite/
repos/oss-cad-suite-*.tgz
repos/iic-osic-tools/

# Simulation artifacts
*.vcd
sim
examples/sim/
examples/*.dot
examples/synth_report.txt

# PowerPoint exports
*.pptx

# Editor
.~lock.*

